text: Crawford County is a county found in the state of Arkansas. At the 2020 census, 60133 people lived in Crawford County. == Cities and towns == These are the cities and towns of Crawford County: * Alma * Cedarville * Chester * Dora * Dyer * Kibler * Mountainburg * Mulberry * Rudy * Van Buren (county seat) == References == == Other websites == * Crawford County government's website Category:Arkansas counties Category:1820 establishments in Arkansas Territory
